## Noncommercial Purposes

Any noncommercial purpose is a permitted purpose.

## Commercial Licensing

For commercial use, contact licensing@juralabs.org

## Free Use Categories

The following uses are explicitly permitted without commercial licence:

- Environmental organisations and charities
- Educational institutions and research
