## Patent Defense

If you make any written claim that the software infringes
or contributes to infringement of any patent, your patent
license for the software granted under these terms ends
immediately. If your company makes such a claim, your
patent license ends immediately for work on behalf of
your company.

## Violations

The first time you are notified in writing that you have
violated any of these terms, or any agreement made under
them, you have 32 calendar days to come into compliance.
If you come into compliance, your license continues as
if you had never broken these terms. If you do not come
into compliance, your licenses end immediately.

